punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_css","title":"Conteúdo CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 60px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#container &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ca0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Exemplo\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#propdef-grid\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Grid Layout<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'grid' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidata a Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Initial value</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code></a>: <code>row</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aplica-se a</th><td>grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Inherited</a></th><td>não</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Percentages</th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Computed value</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: as specified</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code></a>: as specified</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.grid","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Propriedades CSS relacionadas: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\"><code>grid-auto-flow</code></a></li>\n <li>Guia de Layout de Grade: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">Line-based placement with CSS Grid</a></em></li>\n <li>Guia de Layout de Grade: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas#grid_definition_shorthands\">Grid template areas - Grid definition shorthands</a></em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade grid do CSS é uma abreviação das propriedades que definem todas as propriedades da grade explícita (grid-template-rows, grid-template-columns, e grid-template-areas (en-US)), e todas as propriedades implícitas da grade (grid-auto-rows (en-US), grid-auto-columns (en-US), e grid-auto-flow), em uma única declaração.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"grid","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"grid","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"grid","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"grid","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"grid","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"grid","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"grid","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"grid","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"grid","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/css/grid","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/css/grid/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/grid","title":"grid"}],"pageTitle":"grid - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}